Mambobin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya (AM) na Wales suna damuwa "kamar muppets"
Wasu Mambobin Majalisar suna damuwa da shawarar cewa dole ne a canza sunansu ga Mambobin Majalisar Wales (MWP).
Wannan rikice-rikice ya samo asali ne daga shirye-shiryen canza sunan Majalisar zuwa Majalisar Wales.
Mambobin Majalisa na dukkanin siyasa suna damuwa da cewa wannan za a iya yin izgili.
Wani memba na Majalisar Labour ya bayyana cewa kungiyarsa ta damu da "ya yi riki tare da Twp da Pwp".
Ga masu karatu na waje daga Wales: A Wales, twp yana nufin wauta da pwp yana nufin wauta.
Wani memba na Majalisar Wales ya bayyana cewa dukan kungiyarsa ta "m" kuma ya bayar da shawarar madadin.
Wani memba na Wales Conservatory Party ya ce ƙungiyarsa tana "buɗewa" don canza sunan, amma ya nuna cewa ƙananan ƙaura daga MWP zuwa muppet.
A wannan yanayin, maganganun haruffa w a galles yana kama da haruffa ko Turanci na Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar, wanda a halin yanzu ke tsara dokoki don gabatar da canza sunan, ta ce: "Hakika, yanke shawara na ƙarshe game da duk wani bayanin bayani game da sunan membobin Majalisar zai zama batun mambobinsu."
Dokar 2017 na Gwamnatin Wales ta ba Majalisar Wales ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon tattaunawa na jama'a game da shawarwari wanda ya nuna babban goyon baya don kira Majalisar Wales zuwa Majalisar.
Game da batun sunan membobin majalisar, Hukumar ta fi son membobin majalisar Wales (ko WMP), amma zaɓin MWP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya a cikin binciken jama'a.
Da alama membobin majalisar suna bayar da shawarar zabin, amma gwagwarmaya don samun amincewa na iya kawo shugaban majalisar, Elin Jones, wanda ya kamata a aika da dokar game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar game da gyare-gyare za ta hada da wasu canje-canje dangane da aiki na majalisar, kamar dokoki game da rasa mambobin majalisar da kuma zane na tsarin kwamitocin.
Mambobin majalisa za su sami kalma ta ƙarshe a kan tambaya game da yadda ya kamata a kira su lokacin da suke tattaunawa game da dokar.
