Shirye-shiryen Sainsbury's suna haɓaka kasuwar kyakkyawar Birtaniya
Sainsbury's ya sayi Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams, waɗanda suke da ma'aikata da yawa masu sana'a a wuraren da ke cikin style da kyakkyawan kamfanoni.
Don haɓaka muhimmancin kasuwar kyawawan kasuwar Birtaniya, wanda aka ƙidaya akan fam biliyan 2800 da kuma girma wanda ke haɓaka idan aka kwatanta da fashion tallace-tallace da gida, za a gwada mafi girman kyawawan wurare a cikin shagunan 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar kuma, idan sun ci nasara, za a yi haka a cikin ƙarin shagunan shekara mai zuwa.
Zuba jari a cikin kyakkyawa ya zo a lokaci guda kamar yadda wannan supermarket sarkar neman hanyoyi don amfani da sararin samaniya a kan tufafi wanda aka saba amfani da shi ga talabijin, microwave da kuma gida.
Sainsbury's ya bayyana cewa zai sauya bayar da kyau tare da kayayyakin har zuwa 3000, ciki har da alamu kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karo na farko.
Bugu da ƙari, za a ba da sararin samaniya ga nau'ikan L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees, tare da yankuna masu kama da na sauran kamfanoni, kamar jirgin ruwa.
Sakamakon zai kuma sake sake fasalin kayan wasan kwaikwayo na Boutique tare da mafi yawan samfuran dabbobi, wani abu wanda ƙananan abokan ciniki ke buƙata.
Har ila yau, a kan kayan shafawa na The Fragrance Shop zai gwada kwarewa a wurare biyu na Sainsbury, na farko da aka bude a Croydon, kudu a London, makon da ya gabata. Na biyu za a bude a Selly Oak, Birmingham, daga baya wannan shekara.
Kasuwanci na kan layi da kuma canzawa zuwa sayen yau da kullum na ƙananan abinci a cikin shagunan gida suna tilasta su supermarkets su yi ƙoƙari su sa mutane su ziyarci su.
Mike Coupe, daraktan zartarwa na Sainsbury's, ya tabbatar da cewa shagunan za su zama kamar cibiyoyin kasuwanci yayin da supermarket sarkar yayi kokarin yaki da aldi da Lidl rangwame cibiyoyin ta bayar da ƙarin sabis da kayayyakin da ba abinci ba.
Sainsbury's sun hada da tallace-tallace na Argos wurare a daruruwan kamfanoni kuma ya gabatar da hanyoyi daban-daban tun lokacin da ya saya wadannan sarkar shekaru biyu da suka gabata. An dauke cewa wannan ya karfafa tallace-tallace na cin abinci kuma ya kara amfani da wadannan sayen.
Tsohon gwaji na supermarket sarkar don sabunta su kyau sassan da kuma Pharmacy ya kasa.
Sainsbury's ya gwada haɗin gwiwa tare da Boots a farkon 2000, amma haɗin gwiwa ya ƙare bayan tattaunawa game da yadda za a raba kudaden shiga daga wuraren sayar da magunguna a cikin su su supermarkets.
Sabuwar dabarun an gabatar da shi ne bayan sayar da 281 kamfanonin masana'antu daga Sainsbury zuwa Celesio, kamfanin mallakar Lloyds Pharmacy, ta hanyar 125 miliyan fam shekaru uku da suka gabata.
An nuna cewa Lloyds zai shiga cikin shirin, ta ƙara fadi da kewayon alatu iri don kula da fata, kamar La Roche-Posay da Vichy a cikin shagunan shagunan hudu.
Kamar yadda Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury: "Mun canza halayenmu da muhalli na kyawawan wurare don samar da yanayin ga abokan cinikinmu.
Bugu da ƙari, mun saka hannun jari a cikin ƙwararrun ma'aikata wanda zai kasance available don bayar da shawara.
An tsara tayin mu na alama don daidaitawa da duk bukatun. Bugu da ƙari, yanayi mai ban sha'awa da wuri mai dadi ya sa mu zama manufar kyawawan kayayyakin, kalubale ga tsohuwar hanyar sayarwa. "
Peter Jones yana "m" bayan Holly Willoughby ya karya yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Peter Jones, tauraron Dragon's Den, ya tafi "m" bayan Holly Willoughby mai gabatar da TV ya karya yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11 tare da layin kasuwancinsa na rayuwa don mayar da hankali kan sabon kwangilar tare da Marks and Spencer da ITV.
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don sadaukar da alama ta fashion da plugins Truly.
Wannan kasuwanci ya kwatanta da Gwyneth Paltrow Guop.
Mai gabatarwa na This Morning, mai shekaru 37, ya sanar da cewa ya bar kasuwancin Instagram.
Holly Willoughby ya yi fushi da Peter Jones, tauraron Dragon's Den, ya bar kasuwancinsa na rayuwa a cikin minti na ƙarshe don mayar da hankali kan sababbin kwangilar su tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
A cewar kafofin watsa labarun, Jones ya kasance "m" lokacin da 'yar zinare ta talabijin ta yarda cewa sabon yarjejeniyar, wanda aka daraja har zuwa 1.5 miliyan fam, ba su barin lokaci don yin amfani da Truly, alama ta fashion da plugins, a lokacin taron da aka gudanar a ranar Talata a hedkwatar masara a Marlow, Buckhamshire.
Kasuwancin ya kwatanta da Guop na Gwyneth Paltrow kuma ya bayyana shi a matsayin abin da ya fi so don sauke kuɗin Willoughby, game da fam miliyan 11.
Yayin da Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya sanar da cewa ya bar kasuwancin Instagram, Jones ya tafi Birtaniya don zuwa daya daga cikin gidajen hutu.
Kamar yadda wani tushen tambaya ya ce: "Hakika, tare da bambanci, shi ne babban fifiko na Holly.
Zai zama makomarsa na dogon lokaci, wanda zai ci gaba da shi a cikin shekaru biyu masu zuwa.
Ya yanke shawarar barin duk wanda ya damu da shi.
Babu wanda ya yi imani da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, kamar yadda kusa da release.
Akwai kaya mai cike da kaya a Marlow hedkwatar, kayayyakin shirye don sayarwa. "
Masana sun yi imani da cewa fita daga wannan safiya mai gabatarwa, daya daga cikin taurari mafi riba na Birtaniya, zai iya kudin miliyoyin ga kamfanin saboda babban zuba jari a kayayyakin da suka je daga kayayyakin da kuma kyandir zuwa tufafi, da kuma yiwuwar jinkirta karin release.
Zai kuma iya nufin ƙarshen dogon abota.
Willoughby da mijinta, Dan Baldwin, iyaye ne da 'ya'ya uku da kuma shekaru goma da suka ci gaba da dangantaka da Jones da matarsa, Tara Capp.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya hade a matsayin shugaban kasa a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata sun tafi hutu tare kuma Jones yana da rabo na 40% a cikin kamfanin talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadancin alama na M & S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity a cikin ITV Channel.
Wani tushen da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya "ba a tattauna batun kasuwanci ba."
