Sturridge ya karbi tafiya daga Xherdan Shaqiri zuwa wani fiye da mita 27 daga ƙofar Chelsea lokacin da lambar ta kasance 1-0.
Ya sanya ball a gefen hagu tare da touch daya kafin ya jefa shi zuwa mataki na biyu.
Ayyukan ya umarci shi sama da yankin, kuma ya tafi zuwa saman dama kusurwa na cibiyar sadarwa.
A karshe, ball ya wuce a kan Kepa Arrizalage, ya yi ƙoƙari ya dakatar da shi, kuma ya fadi a cikin cibiyar sadarwa.
"Na yi kokarin sanya ni a cikin wannan matsayi don yin ni da ball kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq koyaushe suna wasa sosai gaba, don haka na yi kokarin ba ni duk lokacin da zai yiwu," in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga cewa Kante yana kusa da shi kuma na ba shi taba. Ba na tunanin shi sosai, kawai na jefa harbi."
Chelsea ta lashe 1-0 a kashi na farko bayan da Belgium Star Eden Hazard ya buga wasan kwaikwayo a minti na 25.
