Duk da haka, sauti na jawabin Ri ya bambanta da jawabin shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya gaya wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba zai yiwu ya jagoranci sojojin Koriya ta Arewa zuwa ƙasar Amurka bayan da "muguwar shugaba" Trump, a cikin sojojin kashe kansa, ya kira Kim "mutum roko."
