A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da aka kafa game da wannan: "Za mu iya ɗaukar shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar, ba kome ba."
China da Rasha sun yi ikirarin cewa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya za ta ba Pyongyang lada don ci gabanta.
