Harvard Students yin wani darasi game da yadda za a huta isasshen
Godiya ga wani sabon hanya da aka koyar a wannan shekara a Jami'ar Harvard, duk jami'a dalibai barci more a kan kokarin yaki da girma mace al'adu na nazarin dukan dare shan caffeine.
Wani farfesa ya gano cewa dalibai na daya a duniya jami'a yawanci ba su da ko ra'ayin game da asali kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa na barci a Harvard Medicine School, kuma masanin kwarewa daga Brigham and Women's Hospital sun tsara hanya, an yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko daga cikin aji a Amurka.
Su motsawa don kaddamar da hanya ya fito bayan tattaunawa game da yadda rashin barci ya shafi ilmantarwa.
"A karshen hanya, wata yarinya ta zo kuma ta tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa ta ji wannan yanzu, a cikin shekara ta karshe.
Ya ce babu wanda ya taba gaya masa game da muhimmancin barci, wanda ya yi mamakin ni, "in ji The Telegraph.
The course, a karo na farko da aka koyar a wannan shekara, ya bayyana dalibai da asali ra'ayoyi game da yadda kyau barci al'adu na taimaka wa ilimi da wasanni yi, da kuma inganta gabaɗaya lafiya.
Paul Barreiira, farfesa na likita a Harvard Medicine School da kuma shugaban jami'a kiwon lafiya ayyuka, ya lura cewa jami'a yanke shawarar gabatar da hanya bayan gano cewa dalibai kawai barci a cikin mako.
A hour tsawon hanya ya hada da jerin interactive ayyuka.
A wani sashe, akwai wani hoto na ɗakin barci, inda dalibai click a kan kofi, lu'u-lu'u, wasanni takalma da littattafai cewa sanar da su game da tasirin caffeine da haske, kazalika da tasirin rashin barci a wasanni aiki da kuma muhimmancin kafa wani yau da kullum don barci.
A wani sashe, an sanar da mahalarta game da yadda dogon lokaci rashin barci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, ciwon daji, damuwa da ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, wani harabar icon tare da interactive icons ya motsa mahalarta su yi tunani game da yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canza halayen dalibai nan da nan.
Duk da haka, mun yi imani da cewa suna da hakkin sani, kamar yadda kowa yana da hakkin sanin tasirin lafiyar shan taba," in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce al'adun girman kai na "ci gaba da dare" har yanzu yana wanzuwa kuma ya kara da cewa fasaha na zamani da matsa lamba da ake fuskanta da dalibai suna nufin cewa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Kwancen lokaci da mafarki mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "bincike makamai" na ɗalibai don yaƙi da damuwa, gajiya da damuwa; koda don kauce wa yin nauyi, saboda rashin barci ya sa kwakwalwa ta haifar da jin yunwa, saboda haka suna so su ci duk lokacin.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 na California wanda ke nazarin ilimin kimiyya da ilimin kimiyyar jiki, ya taimaka farfesa Czeisler ya tsara hanya bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin ɗalibansa a shekarar da ta gabata a cikin shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Ya bayyana cewa hanya ya bude idanu a gare shi kuma ya yi wahayi zuwa fadada shi a duk harabar.
Ina fatan mataki na gaba zai zama tambaya dukan digiri dalibai don kammala irin wannan nazarin shirin kafin su shiga gasar ma'aikata.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa dalibai su yi tunani game da sanya ƙararrawa don zuwa gado da sauransu don farka, kuma su kasance da hankali game da sakamako mai cutarwa na "blue light" da ke fitowa da allon lantarki da LEDs, waɗanda zasu iya canza tsaka-tsaki na circadian, don haka za su kawo ƙarshen samun matsala don barci.
