The Global Citizen Festival, wanda ya fara a shekara ta 2012, shi ne tsawo na Global talauci Project, ƙungiyar sadarwa ta duniya da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar karuwar yawan mutanen da suke yaƙi da ita.
