Mai kirkiro na World Wide Web yana shirin fara sabon Intanet don gasa tare da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, mai kirkiro na World Wide Web, yana kaddamar da sabon kamfanin da ke ƙoƙarin rinjayar Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt ne na karshe aikin fasaha legend. A kamfanin da ya dogara a kan bude solid soda soda dandali na Berners-Lee.
Solid ba da damar masu amfani zabi inda za a adana bayanai da kuma wane mutane za su sami damar abin da bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman tare da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi izgili cewa nufin da aka ɓoye a bayan Inrupt shine "mallakar duniya."
"Dole ne ya kasance yanzu," in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi."
A aikace-aikace yana amfani da fasaha na Solid don masu amfani za su iya ƙirƙirar kansu "ajiyar bayanan sirri" ko POD.
Kuna iya ƙunsar jerin, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, library na music da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da masu sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a wani browser kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da yake da musamman a kan sirri online data ajiya shi ne cewa mai amfani ne wanda cikakken yanke shawara wanda zai iya samun damar wane irin bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "Haɓaka na sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Ra'ayin Inrupt, a cewar babban darakta na kamfanin, John Bruce, shine haɗa albarkatu, matakai da basira da ake buƙata don Solid zai iya kaiwa duk duniya.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro wanda ya sayi IBM, wasu daga cikin masu haɓaka da aka haɗa da su don yin aiki a cikin aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirya shirye-shirye.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu ci gaba da fasaha daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar nasu rarraba apps tare da kayan aikin da ke samuwa a kan Inrupt website.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da ƙungiyarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a gabatar da wani canzawa mai mahimmanci inda duk kamfanin model da aka cikakken canza daga rana zuwa wani.
"Ba za mu nemi izini ba."
A wani littafi a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta game da Inrupt cewa "matsayinsa shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da tsarin muhalli don taimakawa kare aminci da ingancin sabon yanar gizon da aka kirkiro a Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya taka muhimmiyar rawa a muhawara game da tsaka-tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Kodayake yana gabatar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance mai kafawa da darakta na World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Open Data.
"Ina matukar fata game da wannan lokaci na gaba na yanar gizo," in ji Berners-Lee.
