Mahukunta na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da ta'addanci a New York
Mahukunta na tarayya na New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargin ta'addanci na birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wani babban hukunci wanda ba a kashe shi a jihar ba saboda laifin tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da ake zargin ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don gudanar da hari a watan Oktoba da ya gabata a kan motar motar motar motar mota a kan hanya ta yammacin gefen Manhattan ta kasa, ta rushe masu yawon bude ido da masu keke da keke da su a kan hanyarsa.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne masu gabatar da kara su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe 'da nufi' wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya haifar da 'da nufi' mummunan rauni na jiki, bisa ga sanarwar da ake nufi da kisa, wanda aka gabatar a yankin Kudancin New York.
Abubuwan da aka zarge su biyu sun haifar da hukuncin kisa, bisa ga hukuncin shari'a.
Bayan makonni da yawa bayan harin, babban rantsuwar tarayya ta gabatar wa Saipov zargin 22 wanda ya hada da zargin kisan kai takwas tare da taimakon laifuka da aka tsara, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da dokokin tarayya a waɗannan lokuta, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da halakar motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsare-tsaren da tsare-tsaren," a cewar mahukunta, waɗanda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi shi a matsayin "mai-mai-yaki, mai-mai-yaki."
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar iyalai da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alexandre Damian Pagnucco."
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Ya riga ya wuce shekaru goma tun lokacin da yankin Kudancin New York ya gabatar da shari'ar hukuncin kisa.
Mai zargin, Khalid Barnes, an yanke masa hukuncin kisan kwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin kurkuku a watan Satumba na 2009.
A karshe lokacin da aka kashe hukuncin kisa a wani tarayya na New York ya zo Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a 1953. An kashe wannan auren bayan da aka yanke musu hukunci da makirci don yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu kafin.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a kan kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
