Yakin ciniki tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya amfana da Beijing
A farko ceto daga cinikayya yakin tsakanin Amurka da kasar Sin sun kasance m, kuma ko da yake har yanzu akwai da yawa don kawo karshen yakin, karshen tsakanin kasashen zai iya amfana da Beijing, masana ra'ayi.
Donald Trump, Shugaban Amurka, ya kaddamar da gargadi na farko a farkon shekara ta hanyar sanya kudade ga manyan fitarwa na kasar Sin, kamar hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi mahimmanci tashi ya faru a wannan makon tare da sababbin kudade wanda ya shafi dala biliyan 200 (150 biliyan fam miliyan) a kayayyakin, wanda ke ɗaukar haraji zuwa rabin kayayyakin shiga Amurka daga kasar Sin.
A duk lokuta, Beijing ta dauki daidaito, kwanan nan ta sanya haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa kashi goma ga kayayyakin Amurka na dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin daidaita kai hare-haren Amurka, kuma ba zai yiwu ba cewa tattalin arziki na biyu mafi girma a duniya zai rage nan da nan.
Samun cewa Washington dawowa yana nufin saduwa da buƙata, amma yin biyayya da Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Duk da haka, masana kimiyya sun ce idan Beijing ta taka leda sosai, matsalolin Amurka na yakin kasuwanci zai iya taimakawa China mai kyau a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dangantaka tsakanin tattalin arziki biyu.
"A gaskiyar cewa wani sauri siyasa yanke shawara a Washington ko Beijing iya sanya ka'idodi don fara faduwar tattalin arziki a kowane kasashe biyu ne a zahiri mafi hadari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka gane har yanzu," in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike mai mayar da hankali a kan batutut na Asia da dabarun hukumar for New American Tsaro Cen.
