Sabunta Ruwan Ruwa: Rage Mayar da hankali a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A sabon rahoto na Florida Fish and Wildlife Commission ( Florida Foundation and Fauna da Florida Commission) yana nuna raguwa gaba ɗaya a cikin tashin hankali a yankunan Tampa.
A cewar FWC, ana sanar da yanayin fure-fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke ba da shawarar rage mayar da hankali.
Ruwan ruwan ja ya fadada kusan 130 mil na bakin teku daga jihar Pinellas zuwa arewa zuwa Lee County zuwa kudu.
Za a iya samun yanki mara kyau a kusa da mita 10 daga bakin teku na Hillsborough County, amma a ƙananan wurare idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
Har ila yau, an gano ruwan ja a cikin Pasco County.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, an sanar da matsakaicin mayar da hankali a cikin Pinellas County da kuma bakin teku, mayar da hankali tsakanin low da high coast a cikin Hillsborough County County, babban mayar da hankali a cikin Manatee County, babban mayar da hankali a cikin Sarasota County da kuma Coast Coast.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton matsalolin numfashi a cikin jihohin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Babu rahotanni game da matsalolin numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
